entry.value: INSERT INTO dom_digital.resumen_log_usabilidad ( WITH resumen as ( SELECT CASE WHEN ABS(DATEDIFF(day,CURRENT_DATE,fecha)) > 2 THEN DATE(created_at) ELSE DATE(fecha) END as fecha, aplicacion, campania, pais_ingreso, region, zona, seccion, usuario, COUNT(usuario) AS total, opcion_pantalla, rol FROM dom_digital.log_usabilidad WHERE process_at is null AND aplicacion in ('APPLIDERES','APPFFVV') AND rol in ('SE','') AND pais_ingreso not in ('VE') GROUP BY 1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,10,11 ) SELECT resumen.fecha, resumen.aplicacion, CASE WHEN campania = '' THEN NULL WHEN campania LIKE '%C%' THEN (extract(year from fecha) || trim(leading 'C' from campania))::int ELSE campania::int END, resumen.pais_ingreso, resumen.region, resumen.zona, resumen.seccion, resumen.usuario, resumen.rol, resumen.opcion_pantalla, resumen.total FROM resumen);
